# Docs — division of truth (canonical)

**Single source for doc boundaries.** Other rules/skills link here; do not duplicate the tables below.

Index: [`Docs/README.md`](Docs/README.md). Workflow: [`vibe-coding-workflow` SKILL](../skills/vibe-coding-workflow/SKILL.md).

**Editing `Docs/Archived/plans/`** — history only; sync checklist **N/A** unless fixing broken links.

---

## Plan file types

| Type | Example | `_Progress.md` | Count at `Docs/` root |
|------|---------|----------------|------------------------|
| **Roadmap plan** | `ci-verification_Plan.md` | No — design reference until kickoff | **Multiple OK** (listed in README) |
| **Task WIP** | Same filename after kickoff | **Required** `{name}_Progress.md` | **One pair max** |

**Kickoff:** user/agent starts implementation → add `_Progress.md`, set README **Active now**. Roadmap plan is the task Plan (no copy/rename required).

**Close:** Closeout → move Plan+Progress to `Archived/plans/`; clear Active now.

---

## Primary home

| Document | Owns | Must NOT own |
|----------|------|--------------|
| **`Active-Plan.md`** | P0–P4 `[ ]`, gates, queue | Diagrams, policy prose, changelogs |
| **`EngineArchitecture.md`** | Diagrams, **locked policies**, risks, non-goals | `[ ]` tasks, sprint logs |
| **`Archived-Plan.md`** | Completed lines; § S1 implementation notes | Open tasks |
| **`Wishlist.md`** | Deferred S4+ until gate opens | Active `[ ]` |
| **`{name}_Plan.md` (roadmap)** | Cross-cutting design before/during epic | Active-Plan duplicates |
| **`{name}_Plan.md` + `_Progress` (WIP)** | One task scope, steps, verification | Roadmap queue |
| **`forward-stage1.md`** | Stage 1 golden / handoff | Sprint queue |
| **Epic plans** (`hybrid-deferred`, `ddgi`) | Stage 2–3 breakdown | P0–P4 checklists |
| **Code** (`Vk_DescriptorPolicy.h`, shaders) | Field layouts, bindings | Scheduling |

---

## When to edit which file

| Change | Edit |
|--------|------|
| Task wording, phase order, gates | `Active-Plan.md` only |
| Task / phase line done | Move → `Archived-Plan.md` |
| **Locked policy** changed (see tree below) | `EngineArchitecture.md` + Active-Plan task (or Wishlist) + code contracts |
| Structure diagram only | `EngineArchitecture.md` only |
| Deferred milestone | `Wishlist.md` |
| UBO field layout only | Code + shader + JSON contract; Architecture **only if policy narrative changes** |

---

## Locked policy? (decision tree)

1. **Layer boundary moved?** (e.g. Gfx may call Vulkan; WorldState owner) → **yes, policy**
2. **Descriptor model changed?** (set roles, dynamic vs push rules) → **yes, policy**
3. **Extract / record contract changed?** (what RecordScenePass may read) → **yes, policy**
4. **Transparent / Stage 2 depth rule changed?** → **yes, policy**
5. **Only struct fields / bindings / shader layout** → **code + MSBuild**; Architecture if (2) narrative shifts
6. **Task done, no 1–4** → Active-Plan → Archived-Plan only

---

## Agent `@`

| Goal | `@` |
|------|-----|
| Next task | `Active-Plan.md` (one P section; grep) |
| Layer / policy | `EngineArchitecture.md` |
| Active WIP steps | `{TaskName}_Plan.md` + `_Progress.md` |
| Roadmap design (pre-kickoff) | e.g. `ci-verification_Plan.md` |
| History | `Archived-Plan.md` / `Archived/plans/` (debug) |

---

## Anti-patterns

- Same table in Active-Plan and Architecture
- Changelog / S2 peel notes in Architecture
- `[ ]` in Architecture
- Architecture edit on every task close
- Second WIP Plan+Progress pair at Docs root
